<PB REF="209" MS="y">
<PB REF="209">
<P>A COLLECTION OF Curious Travels and Voyages.</P>
<P>The Second Tome.</P>
<P>CONTAINING Ob&s;ervations made by &s;e|veral Learned and Famous Men in their Journeys through the <HI>Le|vant,</HI> viz. <HI>the I&s;le of</HI> Candy, Greece, Aegypt, A&s;ia minor, &amp;c. <HI>by Mon|&s;ieur</HI> Belon, Pro&s;per Alpinus, <HI>Dr.</HI> Huntingdon, <HI>Mr.</HI> Vernon, <HI>Sir</HI> George Wheeler, <HI>Dr.</HI> Smith, <HI>Mr.</HI> Greaves, <HI>Father</HI> Van&s;leb, <HI>and</HI> others.</P>
<P>To which are added, Two Itineraries to <HI>Mecha,</HI> and into <HI>Aethiopio.</HI></P>
